Type: Package
Package: coremicrobiota
Title: Core Microbiota Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Anicet Ebou
Maintainer: Anicet Ebou <anicet.ebou@gmail.com>
Description: Computes the core microbiota based on relative sequence
    abundance across all samples and samples ubiquity. This package
    provide also usefull function for plotting and exploring core
    microbiota from a ASV/OTU table.
